            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报9,736.28点，升33.12点(0.34%)；德国DAX指数报24,391.86点，升97.25点(0.40%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,101.83点，升16.07点(0.20%)。 (ST)</span>\n</div>",
